OL,3,CThames Water boss defends #195K bonus
OL,4,Cdespite company's 'excessive' debt
OL,6,FThames Water's chief executive has
OL,7,Fdefended accepting a #195,000 bonus
OL,8,Fjust three months into the job while
OL,9,Fthe company battled "excessive" debts.
OL,11,FChris Weston, alongside chairman Sir
OL,12,FAdrian Montague, and chief financial
OL,13,Fofficer Steve Buck, was being quizzed
OL,14,Fon the water company's "hair-raising"
OL,15,Ffinancial situation by the MPs at the
OL,16,FEnvironment, Food and Rural Affairs
OL,17,FCommittee this morning.
