OL,3,CThames Water boss defends #195K bonus
OL,4,Cdespite company's 'excessive' debt
OL,6,F"It is a big ship to turn around. It
OL,7,Fis very difficult."
OL,9,FWhen asked by MPs about Thames'
OL,10,Ffinances, he admitted on several
OL,11,Foccasions last year Thames Water has
OL,12,Fcome very close to running out of
OL,13,Fmoney entirely.
OL,15,F"There were times in the last year
OL,16,Fthat we had five weeks' liquidity `
OL,17,Fand running a #20 billion corporation
OL,18,Fon five weeks' liquidity, honestly,
OL,19,Fit's hair-raising," Mr Weston said.
