OL,3,CThames Water boss defends #195K bonus
OL,4,Cdespite company's 'excessive' debt
OL,6,FHe also acknowledged his firm's levels
OL,7,Fof debt were "excessive," but said
OL,8,F"debt is a very important part of the
OL,9,Fmodel of the water industry".
OL,11,FDespite the financial issues, the
OL,12,Fbosses said they were prepared for a
OL,13,Fdrought this summer - though it did
OL,14,Fcome "dangerously close" to running
OL,15,Fout of water in the drought summer of
OL,16,F2022 and paying for a #150 million
OL,17,Fdesalination plant that is not working
OL,18,Fyet.
