OL,3,CThames Water boss defends #195K bonus
OL,4,Cdespite company's 'excessive' debt
OL,6,FThames Water's chairman Sir Adrian
OL,7,FMontague then apologised for "letting
OL,8,Fcustomers down".
OL,10,FHe said: "We know that pollutions, we
OL,11,Fknow that spills, we know that supply
OL,12,Finterruptions cause inconvenience and
OL,13,Fsometimes real hardship.
OL,15,F"So I think the right thing to do is
OL,16,Fto start a discussion of the
OL,17,Fturnaround plan by acknowledging that
OL,18,Fwe haven't always served our customers
OL,19,Fas well as we should, and through the
OL,20,Fcommittee apologising to them."
